   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-a" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Huh? Why did I become a thief? Were you previously listening when I was telling my story?<BR>You are annoying!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-b" mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Initially, I wanted to become a wizard. One day, I was doing an experiment something exploded! When regain consious, I was like this. Well, stealing will be the best thing to do with an invisible body, isn't it?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-c" mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>Erm, that's kind of positive.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-e" mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>But, it's still wrong to steal.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-g" mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>Isn't there some ways to return to your original form?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Since this is the case, I might as well become a great thief like Phantom Thief Shupin! Hahahaha!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-d" mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>What? Are you trying to be sarcastic?<BR>Isn't being positive a good thing? Do you think being negative is better?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>When you can't change the reality, you need to adapt to it~<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Invisible Thief seems to be a bit cranky now.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-f" mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>So, you are trying to teach me? Of course stealing is bad!!<BR>But, with body like this, do you think I can still receive any mission? I can't be a wizard anymore, I'll just do whatever I want!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>But.. But.. Wouldn't it be nice to be a helpful great thief like Phantom Thief Shupin?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Invisible Thief in deep thoughts.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-g" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-h" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>I've been trying hard, but it's not that easy.<BR>I even tried painting my body, but when it rains, I turned invisible again.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-accepting-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Some day, I should be able to return to my former self again, right?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Invisible Thief sounds hopeful.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
